<item>
            <title>[DATAREST-373] @HandleBeforeSave RepositoryEventHandler should be able to contain old entity</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/DATAREST-373</link>
                <project id="10901" key="DATAREST">Spring Data REST</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In case of @HandleBeforeSave it&apos;s desired to have the entity object values of the old domain object being updated.&lt;/p&gt;

