&lt;p&gt;In order to keep the prevFamilySize updated I set its value with the actual familySize on the HandleBeforeSave/HandleBeforeCreate events after every processing has been done (is the last thing I do on the events).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p/&gt;
&lt;div id=&quot;syntaxplugin&quot; class=&quot;syntaxplugin&quot; style=&quot;border: 1px dashed #bbb; border-radius: 5px !important; overflow: auto; max-height: 30em;&quot;&gt;
